<b>No, it's not.</b>

1656
01:12:48,800 --> 01:12:50,159
<b>I did not raise my</b>

1657
01:12:50,159 --> 01:12:52,000
<b>daughter to be a lesbian.</b>

1658
01:12:52,000 --> 01:12:53,520
