1681
01:14:20,640 --> 01:14:23,560
<b>biblical thing and disowned me.</b>

1682
01:14:23,560 --> 01:14:24,800
<b>I didn't have to give her time. My mother</b>

1683
01:14:24,800 --> 01:14:25,600
