01:14:59,600 --> 01:15:00,960
<b>What?</b>

1701
01:15:00,960 --> 01:15:02,199
<b>You wouldn't have done it or you wouldn't</b>

1702
01:15:02,199 --> 01:15:03,960
<b>have had feelings for me?</b>

1703
01:15:03,960 --> 01:15:05,399
