1744
01:17:34,800 --> 01:17:40,520
<b>Very confused.</b>

1745
01:17:40,520 --> 01:17:44,960
<b>But what I loved about you when we met,</b>

1746
01:17:46,399 --> 01:17:51,920
<b>I still love about you.</b>

1747
01:17:51,920 --> 01:17:55,600
<b>I want you to be happy.</b>

1748
01:17:55,600 --> 01:18:00,359
<b>And I want to be happy too, so...</b>

1749
01:18:00,359 --> 01:18:02,560
<b>I'm going to try and do better.</b>

1750
01:18:05,840 --> 01:18:11,239
<b>That's all I wanted to say.</b>

