01:18:16,119 --> 01:18:33,279
<b>(Music)</b>

1752
01:18:33,279 --> 01:18:34,039
<b>Hey, beautiful.</b>

1753
01:18:34,039 --> 01:18:36,640
<b>Hi, Mary.</b>

