1793
01:20:44,279 --> 01:20:46,399
<b>This is my graduation.</b>

1794
01:20:47,239 --> 01:20:50,199
<b>And if you don't come, you don't have a</b>

1795
01:20:50,199 --> 01:20:59,119
<b>daughter or a granddaughter.</b>

1796
01:20:59,119 --> 01:21:08,720
<b>It's so much easier, Dorothy, to remember</b>

1797
01:21:08,720 --> 01:21:09,800
<b>why you love someone</b>

1798
01:21:09,800 --> 01:21:11,720
<b>and to move past things,</b>

1799
01:21:12,560 --> 01:21:18,920
