1800
01:21:18,920 --> 01:21:26,319
<b>You can just pretend to, like I'm doing.</b>

1801
01:21:26,319 --> 01:21:30,119
<b>Kate's a remarkable person.</b>

1802
01:21:30,119 --> 01:21:33,319
<b>She gave me that kid.</b>

1803
01:21:33,319 --> 01:21:35,439
<b>Even you have to admit.</b>

1804
01:21:36,640 --> 01:21:40,119
<b>That's some kid.</b>

1805
01:22:36,920 --> 01:22:38,600
<b>We present to you the</b>

1806
01:22:38,600 --> 01:22:41,039
<b>graduating class of 2002.</b>

1807
01:22:43,079 --> 01:22:55,560
<b>[Music]</b>

1808
01:22:55,560 --> 01:23:04,359
<b>I'm very proud of you, Sam, and I love</b>

1809
01:23:04,359 --> 01:23:05,880
<b>you very, very much.</b>

