01:23:24,600 --> 01:23:27,560
<b>mean, you haven't been for a long time.</b>

1818
01:23:27,560 --> 01:23:30,560
<b>That's it. Simple, huh?</b>

1819
01:23:30,560 --> 01:23:34,039
<b>You are a spectacular person.</b>

1820
01:23:36,119 --> 01:23:37,640
<b>You should stop pushing me. I'll get</b>

1821
01:23:37,640 --> 01:23:38,640
