1825
01:23:50,760 --> 01:23:52,439
<b>See you about that. I'm glad you took</b>

1826
01:23:52,439 --> 01:23:53,760
<b>that thing out anyway.</b>

1827
01:23:53,760 --> 01:23:56,079
<b>You're a graduate. Why did you do this?</b>

1828
01:23:56,079 --> 01:23:57,439
<b>Isn't this a foreshadow?</b>

1829
01:23:57,439 --> 01:23:58,920
<b>-Is it? -No, it's permanent.</b>

1830
01:23:59,600 --> 01:24:02,399
